ommercial-carbon-capture-facility-opens-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECarbon%20capture%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20coming%20to%20US%20Steel's%20GaryWorks%20plant%20on%20the%20south%20shore%20of%20Lake%20Michigan%2C%20which%20churns%20out%20the%20steel%20that%20shapes%20modern%20life%2C%20from%20buildings%20and%20bridges%20to%20cars%20and%20wind%20turbines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20production%20comes%20with%20an%20environmental%20cost.%20GaryWorks%20is%20Indiana's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Fghgreporting%2Fghgrp-state-and-tribal-fact-sheet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elargest%20polluter%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20federal%20data%20shows.%20US%20Steel%20said%20it%20can%20cut%20those%20emissions%20by%20about%200.5%25%20a%20year%20by%202026%20using%20technology%20from%20the%20company%20CarbonFree.%20If%20completed%2C%20the%20project%20would%20be%20the%20first%20commercial%20carbon%20capture%20at%20a%20steel%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20progress%2C%20not%20perfection%2C%26quot%3B%20Erika%20Chan%2C%20US%20Steel's%20head%20of%20sustainability%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20excited%20about%20the%20possibilities%20and%20potential.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20potential%20is%20up%20for%20debate.%20Many%20climate%20advocates%20and%20some%20researchers%20warn%20that%20carbon%20capture%20is%20an%20unproven%20distraction%20from%20other%20solutions%20that%20could%20rid%20steelmaking%20of%20a%20lot%20more%20fossil%20fuels%20and%20unhealthy%20pollutants.%20But%20those%20solutions%20are%20also%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20development%2C%20and%20backers%20of%20carbon%20capture%20say%20curbing%20some%20emissions%20now%20is%20better%20than%20none%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20at%20stake%20in%20the%20race%20to%20clean%20up%20steelmaking.%20Globally%2C%20the%20industry%20accounts%20for%208%25%20of%20emissions.%20It's%20also%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdecarbonize-steel-green-uk-scientists-how-to-cut-pollution-steel-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eof%20the%20hardest%20to%20make%20green%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20power%2C%20heat%2C%20and%20coal%20and%20iron%20ore%20in%20most%20cases.%20Governments%20and%20companies%20are%20now%20pouring%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20projects%20trying%20to%20solve%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20its%20part%2C%20CarbonFree%20will%20spend%20about%20%24150%20million%20to%20build%20out%20its%20technology%20at%20GaryWorks%2C%20according%20to%20CEO%20Martin%20Keighley.%20He%20said%20his%20company%20can%20earn%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20returns%26quot%3B%20by%20selling%20calcium%20carbonate%2C%20a%20substance%20made%20from%20the%20captured%20carbon%20and%20other%20chemicals%2C%20to%20manufacturers%20of%20paint%2C%20paper%2C%20plastic%2C%20and%20pharmaceuticals.%20Once%20operational%2C%20CarbonFree%20can%20also%20claim%20about%20%243%20million%20a%20year%20in%20federal%20tax%20breaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%203D%20rendering%20of%20CarbonFree's%20carbon%20capture%20technology%20at%20US%20Steel's%20plant%20in%20Gary%2C%20Indiana.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660d7b693f923f7dab041b3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%203D%20rendering%20of%20where%20CarbonFree's%20carbon%20capture%20technology%20will%20attach%20to%20US%20Steel's%20mill.%3Cp%3ECarbonFree%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKeighley%20said%20an%20outside%20firm%20is%20vetting%20the%20carbon%20capture%20project%20at%20GaryWorks%20to%20verify%20that%20it%20will%20reduce%20emissions%2C%20even%20though%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20gas%20will%20be%20used%20to%20power%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20%E2%80%94%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bp.com%2Fen_us%2Funited-states%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Fcarbonfree-and-bp-collaborate-to-help-bring-carbon-capture-and-utilization-technology-to-industrial-sites-around-the-world.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecounts%20BP%20among%20its%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20won't%20sell%20the%20captured%20carbon%20from%20GaryWorks%20for%20use%20in%20oil%20and%20gas%20production%2C%20Keighley%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20carbon%20captured%20at%20industrial%20sites%20today%20is%20piped%20to%20oil%20fields%20and%20injected%20back%20underground%20to%20squeeze%20out%20more%20oil%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Fghgreporting%2Fsupply-underground-injection-and-geologic-sequestration-carbon-dioxide%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20EPA%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20fuels%20climate%20advocates'%20complaints%20that%20the%20technology%20will%20extend%20the%20life%20of%20the%20industry%20most%20responsible%20for%20the%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Small%20drop%20in%20a%20very%20big%20bucket'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20Inskeep%2C%20the%20program%20director%20of%20Citizens%20Action%20Coalition%20of%20Indiana%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20even%20if%20emissions%20reductions%20are%20realized%20at%20GaryWorks%2C%20it%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20small%20drop%20in%20a%20very%20big%20bucket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20viable%20pathway%20to%20decarbonize%20GaryWorks%2C%26quot%3B%20Inskeep%20said%20of%20carbon%20capture.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20really%20terrible%20pollution%20will%20continue%20and%20this%20carbon%20capture%20project%20won't%20address%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20being%20the%20top%20carbon%20dioxide%20emitter%20in%20Indiana%2C%20GaryWorks%20is%20also%20a%20top%20producer%20of%20other%20harmful%20air%20pollutants%20like%20carbon%20monoxide%20and%20particulate%20matter.%20The%20mill%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobalenergymonitor.org%2Fprojects%2Fglobal-blast-furnace-tracker%2Fsummary-tables%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eamong%20just%2010%20in%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%20still%20using%20blast%20furnaces%20%E2%80%94%20the%20dirtiest%20way%20to%20make%20steel%20because%20they%20burn%20coal%20and%20iron%20ore.%20The%20residents%20of%20Gary%2C%20who%20are%20majority%20Black%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgrist.org%2Fregulation%2Fepa-crackdown-steel-mill-pollution-gary-indiana-lawsuits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eare%20suffering%20from%20the%20health%20effects%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Inskeep%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20advocating%20for%20truly%20sustainable%20steel%20that%20moves%20away%20from%20the%20blast%20furnaces%2C%26quot%3B%20Inskeep%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20American%20steelmakers%20have%20switched%20to%20cleaner%20electric-arc%20furnaces%2C%20which%20melt%20down%20scrap%20metal%20into%20new%20steel.%20There's%20also%20emerging%20technology%20that%20could%20avoid%20coal%20and%20natural%20gas%20altogether%20by%20using%20green%20hydrogen%20and%20renewable%20electricity%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdecarbonize-steel-green-uk-scientists-how-to-cut-pollution-steel-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethough%20it%20hasn't%20reached%20commercial%20scale%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChan%20said%20both%20of%20those%20strategies%20are%20included%20in%20US%20Steel's%20goal%20to%20have%20net-zero%20emissions%20by%202050.%20She%20noted%20that%20US%20Steel%20acquired%20and%20expanded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.localmemphis.com%2Farticle%2Fmoney%2Fus-steel-mill-east-arkansas-economic-impact%2F522-7eb9a294-1a0f-4b38-8e04-5b984acd4af1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20site%20in%20East%20Arkansas%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20electric-arc%20furnaces%20that%20have%2070%25%20to%2080%25%20lower%20emissions%20than%20blast%20furnaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20projects%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20capital%2C%20Chan%20said.%20CarbonFree's%20technology%20doesn't%20require%20US%20Steel%20to%20make%20new%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20American%20steelmaker%2C%20Cleveland%20Cliffs%2C%20in%20March%20announced%20it%20planned%20to%20spend%20about%20%241.4%20billion%20in%20Ohio%20and%20Pennsylvania%20to%20replace%20a%20blast%20furnace%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bhydrogen-ready%26quot%3B%20plant%20and%20electrify%20other%20furnaces.%20The%20plan%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clevelandcliffs.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-releases%2Fdetail%2F629%2Fcleveland-cliffs-selected-to-receive-575-million-in-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtingent%20on%20a%20potentially%20half-billion-dollar%20grant%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInskeep%20said%20he'd%20like%20to%20see%20US%20Steel%20follow%20a%20similar%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20companies%20making%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20profits%20a%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Inskeep%20said.%20%26quot%3BUS%20Steel%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20acquired%2C%20potentially.%20It's%20very%20capable%20of%20making%20very%20large%20investments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChan%20said%20she%20couldn't%20comment%20on%20negotiations%20with%20Nippon%20Steel%2C%20a%20Japanese%20rival%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3Etrying%20to%20take%20over%20the%20company.%20However%2C%20both%20are%20aligned%20on%20making%20climate%20action%20a%20priority%2C%20she%20added.%20The%20deal%20is%20under%20review%20by%20national%20security%20regulators%2C%20although%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20The%20United%20Steelworkers%20union%20have%20opposed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20CarbonFree%20aims%20to%20start%20running%20its%20carbon%20capture%20system%20at%20GaryWorks%20in%202026%20and%20hopes%20to%20expand%20it%20over%20the%2020-year%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20strongly%20that%20in%20the%20next%2020%20to%2030%20years%2C%20we%20will%20still%20be%20releasing%20Co2%20from%20industrial%20steel%2C%20cement%2C%2