r%20a%2020-hour-long%20rescue%20operation%2C%20the%20two-year-old%20boy%20who%20fell%20into%20a%20borewell%20in%20Karnataka's%20Lachyana%20village%20was%20safely%20rescued%20on%20Thursday%20afternoon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fvideo-how-rescue-teams-reached-child-who-fell-in-16-feet-deep-borewell-5373098%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fvideo-how-rescue-teams-reached-child-who-fell-in-16-feet-deep-borewell-5373098%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fvideo-how-rescue-teams-reached-child-who-fell-in-16-feet-deep-borewell-5373098%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%207%2C500%20Trees%20Cut%20For%2016-Km%20Section%20Of%20Delhi-Dehradun%20Expressway%3A%20RTI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%207%2C575%20trees%20have%20been%20felled%20on%20a%20nearly%2016-km-long%20section%20of%20the%20Delhi-Dehradun%20Expressway%20and%20over%201.76%20lakh%20are%20to%20be%20planted%20in%20compensation%20for%20it%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Highways%20Authority%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20felled%20trees%20on%20the%20Ganeshpur-Dehradun%20section%20of%20the%20project%2C%204%2C983%20were%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20while%202%2C592%20were%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20NHAI%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20query%20filed%20under%20provisions%20of%20the%20Right%20To%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20RTI%20query%2C%20Noida-based%20social%20activist%20Amit%20Gupta%20also%20sought%20to%20know%20the%20status%20of%20replantation%20and%20survival%20of%20trees%20on%20the%2015.8-km-long%20section%20of%20the%20Delhi-Dehradun%20Expressway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20response%2C%20Pankaj%20Kumar%20Mourya%2C%20the%20public%20information%20officer-cum-project%20director%2C%20said%20155%20trees%20have%20been%20translocated%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20121%20of%20them%20have%20survived%20the%20translocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20compensatory%20afforestation%20scheme%20submitted%20by%20the%20forest%20departments%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%2C%201%2C76%2C050%20trees%20are%20to%20be%20planted%20by%20them%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20felling%20of%207%2C575%20trees%2C%20the%20NHAI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTotal%20Rs%203%2C60%2C69%2C780%20have%20been%20paid%20against%20compensatory%20afforestation%20to%20forest%20departments%20of%20UP%20and%20Uttarakhand%20by%20the%20NHAI%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20(MoRTH)%2C%20the%20212%20km-long%20six-lane%20Delhi-Dehradun%20Greenfield%20Access%20Controlled%20Expressway%20is%20being%20built%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2012%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expressway%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20cut%20travel%20time%20between%20Delhi%20and%20Dehradun%20to%20two-and-a-half%20hours%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20open%20next%20year%20for%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDivided%20into%20four%20sections%2C%20this%20expressway%20is%20being%20constructed%20starting%20from%20Delhi-Mumbai%20Expressway%20near%20Akshardham%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Shastri%20Park%2C%20Khajuri%20Khas%2C%20EPE%20interchange%20at%20Khekra%20in%20Mandola%2C%20Baghpat%2C%20Shamli%2C%20Saharanpur%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20Dehradun%2C%20Uttrakhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20340-metre-long%20three-lane%20tunnel%20is%20also%20being%20constructed%20at%20Datkali%2C%20Dehradun%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%201%2C995%20crore%2C%20the%20ministry%20stated%20in%20an%20April%202023%20statement%20about%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20special%20provisions%20have%20been%20made%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20entire%20corridor.%20In%20these%2C%20the%20route%20from%20Ganeshpur%20to%20Dehradun%20has%20been%20kept%20safe%20for%20wi