20the%20heart%20of%20the%20checkout-free%20tech%20that%20made%20its%20way%20into%20not%20just%20Amazon%20Fresh%20stores%2C%20first%20launched%20in%202020%2C%20but%20the%20Seahawks%20NFL%20stadium%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20feat%20is%20a%20combination%20of%20computer%20vision%2C%20object%20recognition%2C%20advanced%20sensors%2C%20deep%20machine%20learning%20models%2C%20and%20generative%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20a%20type%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20that%20has%20recently%20captured%20the%20public's%20imagination%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20its%20blog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-fresh-adding-self-checkout-after-trying-just-walk-out-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BJust%20Walk%20Out%26quot%3B%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20almost%2050%20of%20Amazon's%2064%20Fresh%20stores%20across%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK%20paints%20a%20picture%20of%20AI%20with%20a%20key%20caveat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrincipally%2C%20Amazon's%20tech%20made%20the%20checkout-free%20magic%20happen%20in%20part%20thanks%20to%20a%20network%20of%20cameras%20that%20were%20overseen%20by%20over%201%2C000%20people%20in%20India%20who%20spend%20part%20of%20their%20working%20hours%20verifying%20what%20people%20take%20off%20the%20shelves%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Da0522955ad563ab6b58c028cfaca06474c3ceac7d9ebdf8a1aced80799734aba%26postID%3D660d5b38805d055e27829c01%26postSlug%3Damazons-just-walk-out-pullback-shows-ai-way-to-go%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.theinformation.com%252Farticles%252Fhow-amazons-big-bet-on-just-walk-out-stumbled%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20report%20last%20year%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20tasks%2C%20which%20included%20%26quot%3Bmanually%20reviewing%20transactions%20and%20labeling%20images%20from%20videos%26quot%3B%20to%20train%20the%20AI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Da0522955ad563ab6b58c028cfaca06474c3ceac7d9ebdf8a1aced80799734aba%26postID%3D660d5b38805d055e27829c01%26postSlug%3Damazons-just-walk-out-pullback-shows-ai-way-to-go%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.theinformation.com%252Farticles%252Fhow-amazons-big-bet-on-just-walk-out-stumbled%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Information%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20a%20reminder%20to%20the%20tech%20industry%20that%20AI%2C%20a%20technology%20meant%20to%20be%20self-sufficient%20and%20autonomous%2C%20is%20often%20still%20dependent%20on%20a%20labor-intensive%20and%20costly%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Amazon%20has%20denied%20that%20its%20Just%20Walk%20Out%20tech%20%26quot%3Brelies%20on%20human%20reviewers%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20rather%20the%20main%20duties%20of%20its%20team%20in%20India%20was%20to%20%26quot%3Bannotate%20video%20images%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20improve%20the%20machine%20learning%20model%20that%20underpinned%20its%20cashier-less%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BAssociates%20may%20also%20validate%20a%20small%20minority%20of%20shopping%20visits%20where%20our%20computer%20vision%20technology%20cannot%20determine%20with%20complete%20confidence%20an%20individual's%20purchases%2C%26quot%3B%20Amazon%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BJust%20Walk%20Out%20technology%20has%20continued%20to%20scale%20while%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20human%20reviews%20year-over-year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20e-commerce%20giant%20also%20added%20that%20the%20technology%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20offered%20in%20its%20smaller%20Amazon%20Go%20stores%20in%20the%20UK%20as%20well%20as%20other%20third-party%20retailers%20across%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20need%20for%20humans%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20continued%20need%20for%20engineers%20and%20monitoring%20staff%20behind%20Just%20Walk%20Out%20provides%20a%20helpful%20reminder%20that%20human%20input%20is%20still%20required%20in%20an%20age%20when%20AI%20hysteria%20has%20driven%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%3C%2Fspan%3E%20into%20startups%20and%20ideas%20that%20are%20positioning%20AI%20as%20a%20technology%20with%20the%20potential%20to%20completely%20upend%20industries%2C%20replace%20humans%2C%20and%20transform%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarry%20Tan%2C%20president%20of%20the%20startup%20accelerator%20Y%20Combinator%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fgarrytan%2Fstatus%2F1775362374360535208%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereacted%20to%20the%20news%20on%20X%20with%20a%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20which%20he%20described%20the%20autonomous%20checkout%20idea%20being%20%26quot%3Bruined%20by%20a%20professional%20managerial%20class%20that%20decided%20to%20use%20fake%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHonestly%20it%20makes%20me%20sad%20to%20see%20a%20Big%20Tech%20firm%20ruined%20by%20a%20professional%20managerial%20class%20that%20decided%20to%20use%20fake%20AI%2C%20deliver%20a%20terrible%20product%2C%20and%20poison%20an%20entire%20market%20(autonomous%20checkout)%20when%20an%20earnest%20Computer%20Vision-driven%20approach%20could%20have%20reached%20profitable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTzKHKC8BCX%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FTzKHKC8BCX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Garry%20Tan%20%F0%9F%92%A5%E2%99%BB%EF%B8%8F%20e%2Facc%20(%40garrytan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgarrytan%2Fstatus%2F1775362374360535208%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EGary%20Marcus%2C%20AI%20