target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epatrons%20are%20pinched%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too.%20Yes%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20is%20starting%20to%20see%20what%20New%20York%20City%20has%20been%20seeing%3A%20The%20worst%20is%20over.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsumer-confidence-economy-stock-market-gas-prices-eggs-vibes-recession-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUniversity%20of%20Michigan%20Consumer%20Sentiment%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20significant%20improvement%20over%20the%20past%20two%20months%2C%20and%20the%20outlook%20for%20inflation%20continues%20to%20improve.%20This%20is%20fantastic%20news%20for%20the%20country%2C%20but%20as%20analysts%20at%20UBS%20pointed%20out%20in%20a%20recent%20note%20to%20clients%2C%20just%20because%20we're%20not%20feeling%20bad%20doesn't%20mean%20we%20necessarily%20feel%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20encouraging%20developments%20and%20sentiment%20should%20continue%20to%20improve%20as%20disinflation%20progresses%2C%20the%20Fed%20cuts%20rates%20and%20real%20incomes%20keep%20rising%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UBS%20analysts%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIn%20short%2C%20the%20vibecession%20for%20the%20public%20at%20large%20may%20be%20over%2C%20but%20the%20vibespansion%20has%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInflation%20hurts%20everyone%2C%20but%20it%20is%20catastrophic%20for%20people%20who%20are%20just%20getting%20by%20%E2%80%94%20or%20just%20starting%20to%20save%20a%20little%20bit.%20In%20an%20extremely%20cringeworthy%20interview%2C%20WK%20Kellogg%20CEO%20Gary%20Pilnick%20seemed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkelloggs-cereal-for-dinner-meal-backlash-price-inflation-pilnick-money-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexcited%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he%20said%20his%20company's%20cereal-for-dinner%20messaging%20was%20%26quot%3Blanding%20really%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCereal%20for%20dinner%20is%20something%20that%20is%20prob