n-hdfc-merger-icra-124040400465_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsecuritisation-volume-growth-slows-to-4-in-fy24-on-hdfc-merger-icra-124040400465_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsecuritisation-volume-growth-slows-to-4-in-fy24-on-hdfc-merger-icra-124040400465_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-2%20Team%20Member%20Makes%20Final%20Of%20UK's%20Toughest%20TV%20Quiz%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20computational%20science%20graduate%20from%20Kolkata%20has%20answered%20a%20series%20of%20complex%20questions%20as%20part%20of%20his%20university's%20team%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20last%20leg%20of%20what%20is%20among%20television's%20%26quot%3Btoughest%26quot%3B%20quiz%20tournaments%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESourajit%20Debnath%2C%2031%2C%20will%20join%20his%20four-member%20Imperial%20College%20London%20team%20as%20they%20go%20head-to-head%20with%20University%20College%20London%20(UCL)%20in%20the%20BBC's%20'University%20Challenge'%20grand%20final%20to%20be%20telecast%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20clips%20being%20aired%20from%20the%20show%20this%20week%2C%20Debnath%20can%20be%20seen%20dressed%20in%20a%20red%20and%20black%20kurta%20dominating%20a%20set%20of%20bonus%20questions%20on%20BAFTA-winning%20video%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20honoured%20to%20have%20been%20given%20a%20chance%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20history%20of%20this%20long-running%20British%20institution%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Debnath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImperial's%20team%20is%20unusually%20well-rounded%20this%20year%20and%20each%20teammate%20has%20their%20own%20selection%20of%20niches%2C%20or%20specialisms%20to%20borrow%20from%20quiz%20parlance.%20All%20other%20things%20being%20equal%2C%20I'm%20responsible%20for%20covering%20maths%2C%20physics%2C%20and%20general%20science%2C%20along%20with%20pop%20culture%20on%20the%20humanities%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Debnath%20has%20completed%20a%20Master's%20in%20Applied%20Computational%20Science%20and%20Engineering%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Earth%20Science%20and%20Engineering%20at%20Imperial%20College%20London%2C%20a%20degree%20he%20chose%20to%20pivot%20to%20a%20career%20in%20computational%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20he%20was%20a%20space%20scientist%20at%20U.R.%20Rao%20Space%20Centre%2C%20the%20spacecraft-making%20arm%20of%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%2C%20where%20he%20worked%20on%20the%202019%20Indian%20lunar%20lander%2Frover%20mission%20Chandrayaan-2%2C%20among%20other%20spacecraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20graduation%20from%20Imperial%20College%20London%2C%20he%20has%20joined%20an%20Imperial%20start-up%20focused%20on%20geophysics%20algorithms%20operating%20out%20of%20the%20university's%20Royal%20School%20of%20Mines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20UK%20is%20a%20friendly%20and%20welcoming%20country%20for%20students%2C%20but%20it's%20quite%20difficult%20to%20get%20funding%20for%20doctoral%20programmes%20as%20overseas%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20Britain%20as%20a%20higher%20education%20destination%20for%20Indian%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribed%20by%20the%20BBC%20as%20%26quot%3BTV's%20toughest%20quiz%20team%20tournament%26quot%3B%2C%20'University%20Challenge'%20is%20hosted%20by%20British%20Indian%20broadcaster%20Amol%20Rajan%20and%20attracts%20teams%20of%20students%20representing%20the%20top%20universities%20from%20across%20the%20UK%20to%20be%20crowned%20quiz%20champions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20semi-final%20against%20the%20University%20of%20Manchester%20last%20week%2C%20Mr%20Debnath%20answered%20several%20challenging%20questions%20including%20one%20with%20an%20Indian%20touch%20that%20sought%20the%20name%20of%20the%20ingredient%20of%20panch%20phoron%20(five-spice%20blend)%20from%20this%20description%3A%20%26quot%3Bthe%20small%20seed%20like%20fruits%20of%20a%20plant%20in%20the%20parsley%20family%20known%20in%20Hindi%20as%20Jeera%26quot%3B%3F%20The%20answer%2C%20cumin%2C%20was%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20easiest%20the%20Bengali%20student%20has%20faced%20so%20far%20in%20the%20tough%20competition.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712221620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fhbr349ms_sourajit-debnath-indian-science-student-linkedin_625x300_04_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fchandrayaan-2-team-member-makes-final-of-uks-toughest-tv-quiz-5372388%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20computational%20science%20graduate%20from%20Kolkata%20has%20answered%20a%20series%20of%20complex%20questions%20as%20part%20of%20his%20university's%20team%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20last%20leg%20of%20what%20is%20among%20television's%20%26quot%3Btoughest%26quot%3B%20quiz%20tournaments%20in%20the%20UK.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fchandrayaan-2-team-member-makes-final-of-uks-toughest-tv-quiz-5372388%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fchandrayaan-2-team-member-makes-final-of-uks-toughest-tv-quiz-5372388%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fchandrayaan-2-team-member-makes-final-of-uks-toughest-tv-quiz-5372388%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Czechs%20to%20give%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20euros%20for%20Ukraine%20ammunition%20plan%2C%20PM%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712221544000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%