Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Frashtriya-lok-dal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%3C%2Fa%3E%20chief%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fjayant-chaudhary%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJayant%20Chaudhary%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20mocked%20former%20ally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fakhilesh-yadav%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20speculation%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsamajwadi-party%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESamajwadi%20Party%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20replace%20-%20a%20second%20time%20-%20its%20candidate%20for%20the%20Meerut%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20RLD%20boss%20posted%20a%20brief%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20'congratulating'%20the%20%26quot%3Blucky%20ones%20in%20the%20opposition%20(who)%20will%20get%20a%20chance%2C%20for%20a%20few%20hours%26quot%3B%20to%20contest%20in%20the%202024%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20those%20who%20did%20not%20get%20tickets%2C%20their%20fate%20is...%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chaudhary's%20jab%20came%20hours%20after%20talk%20the%20SP%20could%20replace%20its%20second-choice%20Meerut%20candidate%20Atul%20Pradhan%20with%20a%20third-choice%20-%20Sunita%20Verma.%20The%20party%20last%20week%20named%20Bhanu%20Pratap%20Singh%20for%20the%20contest%2C%20but%20backed%20down%20after%20local%20leaders%20signaled%20unease%20with%20the%20choice%20of%20an%20'outsider'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%20was%20personally%20involved%20in%20the%20first%20course%20correction%2C%20sources%20have%20indicated%2C%20meeting%20with%20local%20leaders%20to%20understand%20their%20concerns%2C%20and%20pulled%20the%20trigger%20for%20second%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party's%20second%20choice%20-%20Mr%20Pradhan%20-%20is%20the%20MLA%20from%20UP's%20Sardhana%20Assembly%20segment.%20Its%20third%20choice%20-%20Mrs%20Verma%20-%20is%20a%20former%20Mayor%20and%20the%20wife%20of%20two-time%20MLA%20Yogesh%20Verma%3B%20both%20were%20expelled%20from%20Mayawati's%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20in%202019%20and%20joined%20the%20SP%20two%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20swap%20-%20fielding%20Mrs%20Verma%20-%20is%20because%20she%20is%20a%20Dalit%20candidate%20and%20Meerut%20is%20home%20to%20around%20four%20lakh%20Dalits.%20Mr%20Pradhan%20is%20from%20the%20Gujjar%20community%2C%20of%20whom%20there%20are%20less%20than%20a%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meerut%20seat%20has%20been%20a%20BJP%20stronghold%20for%20the%20past%2015%20years%3B%20Rajendra%20Agarwal%20has%20held%20this%20seat%20for%20the%20saffron%20party%20since%202009.%20Mr%20Agarwal%2C%20though%2C%20is%20not%20in%20line%20for%20a%20fourth%20consecutive%20win%20because%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Farun-govil%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArun%20Govil%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20played%20Lord%20Ram%20in%20the%20popular%20TV%20series%20Ramayana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Govil%20is%20part%20of%20the%20BJP's%20calculated%20push%20in%20western%20UP%2C%20where%20the%20party%20faltered%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FJayant%2520Chaudhary%2527s%2520Rashtriya%2520Lok%2520Dal%2520Formally%2520Joins%2520BJP-Led%2520NDA%2520Alliance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJayant%20Chaudhary's%20RLD%20Formally%20Joins%20BJP-Led%20NDA%20Alliance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBringing%20Mr%20Chaudhary%20on%20board%20is%20crucial%20in%20that%20context%2C%20since%20the%20RLD%20has%20sway%20among%20Jats%20and%20farmers%20in%20that%20region.%20The%20RLD%20and%20the%20BJP%20reached%20an%20agreement%20in%20February%2C%20a%20month%20after%20Mr%20Chaudhary%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20struck%20a%20deal.%20The%20switch%20came%20after%20the%20BJP%20awarded%20a%20posthumous%20Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20Mr%20Chuadhary's%20grandfather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchaudhary-charan-singh-bharat-ratna-jayant-chaudhary-rld-bjp-alliance-dil-jeet-liya-rld-leader-as-pm-announces-bharat-ratna-for-charan-singh-5024116%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BDil%20Jeet%20Liya%26quot%3B%3A%20RLD%20Leader%20As%20PM%20Awads%20Bharat%20Ratna%20To%20Charan%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20election%20the%20BJP%20won%20only%2019%20of%2027%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20western%20UP%20-%20down%20from%2024%20in%202014.%20The%20BJP%20has%20set%20itself%20a%20target%20of%20370%2B%20seats%20on%20its%20own%20in%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20that%20goal%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20need%20to%20maximise%20returns%20from%20UP%2C%20a%20state%20that%20sends%2080%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20one%20which%20has%20been%20the%20party's%20unshakeable%20bastion%20in%20recent%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20those%2080%20seats%20will%20be%20contested%20by%20the%20RLD%3B%20Bijnor%20and%20Baghpat%20have%20been%20allotted%20to%20the%20party%2C%20and%20Chandan%20Chauhan%20and%20Rajkumar%20Sangwan%20have%20been%20named%20its%20candidates.%20The%20latter%20is%20crucial%20since%20it%C2%A0is%20viewed%20as%20a%20stronghold%20of%20Mr%20Chaudhary's%20family%3B%20it%20elected%20his%20father%20Ajit%20Singh%20seven%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjayant-chaudhary-rld-names-candidates-for-baghpat-bijnor-lok-sabha-seats-it-got-in-deal-with-bjp-5175184%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERLD%20Names%20Candidates%20For%202%20Lok%20Sabha%20Seats%20It%20Got%20In%20Deal%20With%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20will%20vote%20in%20all%20seven%20phases%20of%20the%202024%20election%