Nirupam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712220106000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109030966%2Cimgsize-927129.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F5-power-centres-in-congress-sonia-rahul-and-priyanka-have-their-own-lobbies-sanjay-nirupam%2Farticleshow%2F109030561.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F5-power-centres-in-congress-sonia-rahul-and-priyanka-have-their-own-lobbies-sanjay-nirupam%2Farticleshow%2F109030561.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jon%20Bernthal%20returns%20to%20MCU%20as%20The%20Punisher%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712220097000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109021912%2Cimgsize-37550.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Fdaredevil-born-again-jon-bernthal-returns-to-mcu-as-the-punisher-alongside-charlie-cox-in-leaked-photos-and-videos%2Farticleshow%2F109021974.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109021974.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENew%20set%20photos%20and%20a%20brief%20video%20from%20the%20upcoming%20series%20Daredevil%3A%20Born%20Again%20have%20surfaced%2C%20offering%20tantalizing%20glimpses%20into%20what's%20in%20store%20for%20the%20highly%20anticipated%20show.%20The%20photos%20reveal%20a%20bruised%20and%20bloodied%20Punisher%2C%20in%20his%20iconic%20skull%20vest%20standing%20beside%20Charlie%20Cox's%20Daredevil%2C%20hinting%20at%20intense%20action%20sequences%20to%20come.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Fdaredevil-born-again-jon-bernthal-returns-to-mcu-as-the-punisher-alongside-charlie-cox-in-leaked-photos-and-videos%2Farticleshow%2F109021974.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Forget%20Bats%20And%20Rats%2C%20This%20'Animal'%20Spreads%20More%20Viruses%20Than%20Any%20Other%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20animals%20like%20rats%20and%20bats%20have%20been%20blamed%20for%20spreading%20diseases%20to%20humans.%20However%2C%20a%20new%20study%20reveals%20a%20surprising%20truth%3A%20humans%20are%20actually%20the%20bigger%20threat%2C%20passing%20nearly%20twice%20as%20many%20viruses%20to%20other%20animals%20as%20we%20receive%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearchers%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ucl.ac.uk%2Fnews%2F2024%2Fmar%2Fhumans-pass-more-viruses-other-animals-we-catch-them%5C%22%3EUniversity%20College%20London%3C%2Fa%3E%20analysed%20viral%20genomes%20and%20found%20that%20in%20most%20cases%20(64%25)%2C%20viruses%20jumped%20from%20humans%20to%20other%20animals%20(anthroponosis).%20This%20makes%20sense%20considering%20our%20vast%20population%20and%20global%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20activities%20also%20contribute%20to%20the%20spread.%20Habitat%20destruction%20and%20pollution%20stress%20animals%2C%20making%20them%20more%20susceptible%20to%20the%20viruses%20we%20carry.%20This%20creates%20a%20double%20threat%3A%20viruses%20can%20evolve%20in%20these%20new%20hosts%20and%20potentially%20spill%20back%20to%20humans%20or%20continue%20to%20threaten%20endangered%20species.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECo-author%20Professor%20Francois%20Balloux%20(UCL%20Genetics%20Institute)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ucl.ac.uk%2Fnews%2F2024%2Fmar%2Fhumans-pass-more-viruses-other-animals-we-catch-them%5C%22%3Esaid%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20consider%20humans%20just%20as%20one%20node%20in%20a%20vast%20network%20of%20hosts%20endlessly%20exchanging%20pathogens%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20sink%20for%20zoonotic%20bugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20surveying%20and%20monitoring%20the%20transmission%20of%20viruses%20between%20animals%20and%20humans%20in%20either%20direction%2C%20we%20can%20better%20understand%20viral%20evolution%20and%20hopefully%20be%20more%20prepared%20for%20future%20outbreaks%20and%20epidemics%20of%20novel%20illnesses%2C%20while%20also%20aiding%20conservation%20efforts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20good%20news%3F%20Viruses%20that%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20jump%20species%20mutate%20faster.%20By%20monitoring%20these%20mutations%2C%20scientists%20can%20identify%20viruses%20with%20higher%20zoonotic%20potential%20(the%20ability%20to%20infect%20humans).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELead%20author%20and%20PhD%20student%20Cedric%20Tan%20(UCL%20Genetics%20Institute%20and%20Francis%20Crick%20Institute)%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWhen%20animals%20catch%20viruses%20from%20humans%2C%20this%20can%20not%20only%20harm%20the%20animal%20and%20potentially%20pose%20a%20conservation%20threat%20to%20the%20species%2C%20but%20it%20may%20also%20cause%20new%20problems%20for%20humans%20by%20impacting%20food%20security%20if%20large%20numbers%20of%20livestock%20need%20to%20be%20culled%20to%20prevent%20an%20epidemic%2C%20as%20has%20been%20happening%20over%20recent%20years%20with%20the%20H5N1%20bird%20flu%20strain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20if%20a%20virus%20carried%20by%20humans%20infects%20a%20new%20animal%20species%2C%20the%20virus%20might%20continue%20to%20thrive%20even%20if%20eradicated%20among%20humans%20or%20even%20evolve%20new%20adaptations%20before%20it%20winds%20up%20infecting%20humans%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnderstanding%20how%20and%20why%20viruses%20evolve%20to%20jump%20into%20different%20hosts%20across%20the%20wider%20tree%20of%20life%20may%20help%20us%20figure%20out%20how%20new%20viral%20diseases%20emerge%20in%20humans%20and%20animals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20research%2C%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41559-024-02353-4%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENature%20Ecology%20%26amp%3B%20Evolution%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20highlights%20the%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20human-to-animal%20viral%20transmission.%20Understanding%20these%20dynamics%20is%20crucial%20for%20protecting%20both%20human%20and%20animal%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712219700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-08%2Fsj8nqggg_rats-generic-mice-generic_625x300_08_August_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fforget-rats-and-bats-this-animal-spreads-more-viruses-than-any-other-5372698%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20study%20reveals%20a%20surprising%20fact%3A%20humans%20are%20actually%20spreading%20more%20viruses%20to%20animals%20than%20we%20receive%20from%20them.%20This%20is%20due%20to%20our%20large%20population%20size%2C%20global%20reach%2C%20and%20activities%20that%20stress%20wildlife.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fforget-rats-and-bats-this-animal-spreads-more-viruses-than-any-other-5372698%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fforget-rats-and-bats-this-animal-spreads-more-viruses-than-any-other-5372698%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fforget-rats-and-bats-this-animal-spreads-more-viruses-than-any-other-5372698%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BMW%20India%20commences%20bookings%20for%20i5%20M60%20EV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712219466000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109030617%2Cimgsize-111422.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fcars%2Fbmw-india-commences-bookings-for-stunning-601-hp-i5-m60-ev-516-km-range-0-100-kmph-in-3-8s-and-more%2Farticleshow%2F109030540.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BMW%20intro