rvative%20Party%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20holding%20power%20in%20the%20UK%20Parliament%20for%20nearly%2015%20years%2C%20the%20Rishi%20Sunak-led%20Conservative%20Party%20expects%20a%20massive%20defeat%20against%20the%20Labour%20Party%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%20It%20reflects%20the%20public's%20growing%20dissatisfaction%20with%20the%20UK's%20worsening%20condition%20-%20repeated%20policy%20failures%2C%20unfulfilled%20promises%2C%20and%20rising%20cost%20of%20living.%20As%20the%20country%20battles%20recession%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20risks%20losing%20his%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20public%20survey%20conducted%20by%20YouGov%2C%20interviewing%2018%2C761%20British%20adults%20between%20March%207-27%2C%20indicates%20a%20landslide%20victory%20for%20the%20Labour%20Party.%20To%20win%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20UK%20Parliament%2C%20parties%20have%20to%20secure%20326%20out%20of%20650%20seats.%20Labour%20is%20projected%20to%20secure%20403%20seats%20nationwide.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Conservatives%20are%20only%20predicted%20to%20win%20155%20seats.%20This%20puts%20them%20at%20169%20seats%20lower%20than%20the%20previous%20YouGov%20MRP%20released%20in%20January%202024.%20YouGov%20claims%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20coming%20tidal%20wave%20projected%20by%20this%20model%20would%20sweep%20away%20several%20major%20Conservative%20figures.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoll%20of%20Polls%20in%20Politico%20highlights%20similar%20trends%2C%20with%2044%25%20of%20people%20intending%20to%20vote%20for%20Labour%20while%20Conservatives%20tail%20behind%20at%2023%25%2C%20as%20of%20March%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sunak's%20campaign%20outlines%20the%20Conservative%20Party's%20goals%20-%20to%20halve%20inflation%2C%20reduce%20national%20debt%2C%20improve%20the%20National%20Health%20Service%20(NHS)%2C%20stop%20illegal%20migrants%2C%20and%20better%20the%20economy.%20Various%20measures%20like%20hikes%20in%20immigration%20costs%20and%20stricter%20refugee%20deportation%20laws%20have%20been%20tried%2C%20but%20have%20proven%20unsuccessful.%20He%20also%20announced%20tax%20cuts%20in%20March.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20Conservatives%20are%20expecting%20defeat%20in%20the%20local%20council%20and%20mayoral%20polls%20to%20be%20held%20on%20May%202.%20Rising%20disapproval%20of%20his%20leadership%20among%20party%20MPs%20may%20lead%20to%20Mr%20Sunak%20facing%20a%20confidence%20vote%20soon%2C%20with%2053%20MP%20signatures%20needed%20to%20oust%20him%20on%20grounds%20of%20no-confidence.%20Mr%20Sunak%20is%20an%20unelected%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20assuming%20the%20role%20after%20ex-PM%20Liz%20Truss'%206-week%20tenure%20ended%20in%20her%20resignation.%20This%20adds%20to%20the%20sharp%20decline%20in%20his%20popularity%20and%20lack%20of%20trust%20in%20his%20capabilities%20as%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Leader%20of%20Labour%20Party%20Keir%20Starmer%20has%20pledged%20that%20the%20opposition%20plans%20to%20lower%20national%20strain%20by%20increasing%20spending%20on%20sectors%20like%20housing%2C%20transport%2C%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20to%20reduce%20inflation%20and%20stabilise%20the%20economy.%20This%20stands%20as%20an%20implicit%20critique%20of%20the%20Conservatives%20who%20have%20failed%20to%20tackle%20these%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Labour%20Party%20has%20also%20called%20on%20Mr%20Sunak%20to%20set%20a%20date%20for%20the%20UK%20General%20Elections%2C%20which%20remains%20decided.%20On%20March%2015%2C%20Labour%20activists%20staged%20a%20demonstration%20at%20Westminster%2C%20dressed%20as%20chickens%20and%20holding%20signs%20reading%20%26quot%3BRishi%2C%20name%20the%20date%20now!%26quot%3B%2C%20to%20mock%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20his%20failure%20to%20do%20so%20yet.%20The%20Fixed-term%20Parliaments%20Act%20in%202022%20restored%20British%20prime%20ministers'%20ability%20to%20set%20election%20dates.%20However%2C%20General%20Elections%20have%20to%20be%20held%20every%205%20years%2C%20so%20Mr%20Sunak%20has%20to%20set%20a%20date%20by%20January%202025.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20public%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20government%20culminates%20and%20polls%20indicate%20a%20decisive%20loss%20for%20the%20Conservatives%2C%20it%20is%20highly%20unlikely%20that%20Mr%20Sunak%20will%20retain%20his%20seat%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20another%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712218860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F6om28o0g_rishi-sunak-reuters_625x300_12_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcrushing-loss-in-uk-polls-predicted-for-rishi-sunak-led-conservative-party-5372671%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20holding%20power%20in%20the%20UK%20Parliament%20for%20nearly%2015%20years%2C%20the%20Rishi%20Sunak-led%20Conservative%20Party%20expects%20a%20massive%20defeat%20against%20the%20Labour%20Party%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcrushing-loss-in-uk-polls-predicted-for-rishi-sunak-led-conservative-party-5372671%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcrushing-loss-in-uk-polls-predicted-for-rishi-sunak-led-conservative-party-5372671%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcrushing-loss-in-uk-polls-predicted-for-rishi-sunak-led-conservative-party-5372671%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22David%20Wenham%20to%20Star%20in%20%E2%80%98SPIT%2C%E2%80%99%20Sequel%20to%20Australian%20Hit%20Film%20%E2%80%98Gettin%E2%80%99%20Square%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712218836000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDavidWenham_GettinSquare-cr.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235960135%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CLord%20of%20th