urjewala%20Tears%20Into%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnder%20fire%20from%20BJP%20for%20his%20remarks%20on%20actor-politician%20Hema%20Malini%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Randeep%20Singh%20Surjewala%20has%20said%20the%20BJP's%20IT%20cell%20has%20developed%20a%20habit%20of%20distorting%20facts%20and%20spreading%20lies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20BJP%20leader%20Amit%20Malviya%20shared%20a%20video%20in%20which%20Mr%20Surjewala%20is%20seen%20addressing%20a%20public%20gathering.%20While%20saying%20that%20people%20elect%20leaders%20to%20raise%20their%20issues%2C%20he%20makes%20a%20remark%20on%20Ms%20Malini.%20In%20his%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Malviya%20said%20it%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20disgusting%20description%20someone%20can%20come%20up%20with%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Congress.%20It%20is%20misogynistic%20and%20abhors%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Malviya%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20row%20surrounding%20offensive%20posts%20against%20actor%20and%20BJP%20candidate%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20from%20the%20social%20media%20profiles%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Supriya%20Shrinate.%20Ms%20Shrinate%20has%20said%20the%20posts%20were%20made%20without%20her%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Surjewala%20today%20shared%20a%20video%20from%20the%20same%20event%2C%20in%20which%20he%20is%20heard%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20respect%20Hema%20Malini%20ji%20because%20she%20is%20married%20to%20Dharmendra%20ji%2C%20she%20is%20our%20bahu.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20twisting%20facts%20and%20spreading%20lies%2C%20he%20said%20the%20ruling%20party's%20objective%20is%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government's%20%26quot%3Banti-youth%2C%20anti-farmer%2C%20anti-poor%20policies%20and%20its%20conspiracy%20to%20finish%20the%20Constitution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20pawns%20of%20BJP%20never%20asked%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20why%20he%20said%20'50%20crore%20ki%20girlfriend'%2C%20called%20a%20woman%20MP%20'Surpanakha'%2C%20trolled%20a%20woman%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20used%20the%20expression%20'Congress's%20widow'%20and%20described%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20as%20a%20'jersey%20cow'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Surjewala%20said%20he%20only%20meant%20that%20every%20elected%20representative%20should%20be%20accountable%20to%20the%20people%2C%20be%20it%20him%20or%20(Haryana%20Chief%20Minister)%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20and%20(BJP%20leader)%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20intention%20was%20not%20to%20insult%20Hema%20Malini%20ji%20or%20to%20hurt%20anybody.%20That's%20why%20I%20clearly%20said%20we%20respect%20Hema%20Malini%20ji%20and%20she%20is%20our%20bahu.%20The%20BJP%20is%20anti-women%2C%20so%20it%20sees%20everything%20from%20its%20misogyny-tinted%20glasses%20and%20conveniently%20spreads%20lies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Malini%20has%20not%20responded%20to%20the%20row%20over%20Mr%20Surjewala's%20remarks.%20She%20is%20currently%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20contest%20in%20Mathura%2C%20which%20she%20has%20represented%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20Mr%20Surjewala%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Shehzad%20Poonawalla%20said%20the%20only%20identity%20of%20the%20Congress%20is%20disrespecting%20the%20'Nari%20Shakti'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNari%20Shakti%20Apmaan%20is%20the%20Congress's%20only%20Penchan.%20And%20this%20has%20been%20yet%20again%20proved%20by%20cruel%2C%20crude%2C%20disgusting%2C%20misogynist%20and%20sexist%20statements%20by%20Surjewala%2C%20and%20those%20statements%20cannot%20even%20be%20repeated%20what%20he%20has%20said%20for%20Hema%20Malini%20ji%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Surjewala%2C%20a%20Congress%20general%20secretary%2C%20is%20the%20latest%20prominent%20leader%20to%20make%20headlines%20for%20his%20remarks%20in%20this%20election%20season.%20Earlier%2C%20his%20party%20colleague%20Ms%20Shrinate%20and%20the%20BJP's%20Dilip%20Ghosh%20have%20been%20warned%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20for%20their%20remarks%20and%20social%20media%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712218200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fmh1r4d68_randeep-surjewala_625x300_04_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frandeep-surjewala-amit-malviya-hema-malini-slammed-for-hema-malini-remark-congress-randeep-surjewala-tears-into-bjp-5372578%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Under%20fire%20from%20BJP%20for%20his%20remarks%20on%20actor-politician%20Hema%20Malini%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Randeep%20Singh%20Surjewala%20has%20said%20the%20BJP's%20IT%20cell%20has%20developed%20a%20habit%20of%20distorting%20facts%20and%20spreading%20lies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frandeep-surjewala-amit-malviya-hema-malini-slammed-for-hema-malini-remark-congress-randeep-surjewala-tears-into-bjp-5372578%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frandeep-surjewala-amit-malviya-hema-malini-slammed-for-hema-malini-remark-congress-randeep-surjewala-tears-into-bjp-5372578%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frandeep-surjewala-amit-malviya-hema-malini-slammed-for-hema-malini-remark-congress-randeep-surjewala-tears-into-bjp-5372578%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Record%20demand%20for%20exports%20spurs%20India's%20services%20PMI%20to%2061.2%20in%20March%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712217941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-07%2F05%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1688580744-8663.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fecono