Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Falia-bhatt-to-play-a-jazz-singer-in-sanjay-leela-bhansalis-love-and-war-co-starring-ranbir-kapoor-vicky-kaushal-report%2Farticleshow%2F109029403.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20quit%20my%20tech%20job%20to%20be%20a%20stay-at-home%20boyfriend%20who%20cooks%2C%20cleans%2C%20and%20sews%20for%20my%20girlfriend.%20I%20have%20no%20plans%20to%20return%20to%20the%209%20to%205.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22William%20Conrad%20and%20girlfriend%20Levi%20Coralynn%20(left)%20Conrad%20holding%20a%20tray%20of%20food.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660bdb541caec1275a6bad0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWilliam%20Conrad%2C%2025%2C%20and%20girlfriend%20Levi%20Coralynn%2C%2026%20(left).%20Conrad%20makes%20most%20of%20the%20couple's%20meals.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Conrad%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWilliam%20Conrad%2C%2025%2C%20and%20his%20girlfriend%20Levi%20Coralynn%2C%2026%2C%20have%20been%20together%20for%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EConrad%20is%20a%20stay-at-home-boyfriend%2C%20while%20Coralynn%2C%20a%20content%20creator%2C%20supports%20them%20financially.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EConrad%20previously%20worked%20in%20tech%20but%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20return.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20William%20Conrad%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20stay-at-home%20boyfriend%20and%20content%20creator%20from%20Canada.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20I've%20been%20a%20stay-at-home%20boyfriend.%20I%20cook%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20do%20the%20laundry%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I've%20never%20been%20happier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20girlfriend%20Levi%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-changes-his-mind-not-anyone-can-succeed-as-influencers-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebig%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20makes%20enough%20to%20provide%20for%20us%20both%20financially.%20She%20works%20from%20home%2C%20and%20I%20do%2090%25%20of%20the%20domestic%20chores.%20Our%20dynamic%20very%20much%20flips%20societal%20norm%20on%20its%20head%2C%20but%20it%20works%20for%20us%2C%20and%20we%20love%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20typical%20day%20I%20wake%20up%20a%20little%20earlier%20than%20Levi%20to%20make%20us%20some%20coffee.%20We%20usually%20share%20a%20coffee%2C%20hang%20out%20for%20a%20while%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwordle-game-viral-experts-psychology-sharing-twitter-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edo%20Wordle%20%3C%2Fa%3Etogether.%20Then%2C%20she'll%20do%20some%20work%20while%20I%20either%20prepare%20food%20or%20do%20other%20household%20chores.%20If%20we're%20not%20ready%20to%20eat%2C%20I%20might%20do%20some%20work%20on%20the%20computer%20alongside%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20she%20works%20from%20home%2C%20we%20pretty%20much%20spend%20every%20minute%20of%20every%20day%20together%2C%20which%20I%20love%20because%20she's%20my%20best%20friend%20before%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20lead%20a%20very%20communal%20life%2C%20and%20that%20applies%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-write-advice-column-relationships-and-money-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20navigate%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20too.%20We've%20never%20had%20the%20perspective%20of%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20my%20money%2C%20this%20is%20your%20money.%26quot%3B%20It's%20very%20much%20a%20joint%20venture%2C%20and%20most%20of%20our%20purchases%20are%20done%20together%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20help%20with%20the%20backend%20of%20her%20business%2C%20doing%20the%20accounts%20and%20bookkeeping%2C%20just%20as%20much%20as%20I%20do%20things%20around%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBeing%20a%20stay-at-home%20boyfriend%20allows%20me%20to%20do%20what%20I%20love%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELevi%20and%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-apps-deleted-hinge-raya-tinder-bumble-oversaturated-bad-matches-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emet%20on%20Hinge%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20three%20years%20ago%20when%20we%20were%20living%20in%20different%20cities.%20I%20was%20living%20in%20Toronto%2C%20near%20where%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20while%20she%20was%20in%20Alberta.%20We%20started%20talking%20online%20and%20knew%20we%20needed%20to%20meet%20in%20person%2C%20so%20she%20came%20to%20see%20me%20in%20Toronto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20date%20was%20a%20week%20long%20and%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopened-three-airbnbs-one-year-advice-getting-started-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estayed%20in%20an%20Airbnb%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Shortly%20after%20that%2C%20we%20moved%20in%20together%20in%20Ontario%2C%20and%20we've%20been%20together%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20sit%20in%20an%20office%20all%20day%20looking%20at%20a%20monitor.%20I've%20always%20liked%20creating%20things%20and%20working%20with%20my%20hands.%20But%20I%20ended%20up%20studying%20computer%20science%20at%20college%20and%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-find-your-next-job-resources-for-job-hunt-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%20a%20job%20at%20a%20tech%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20met%20Levi%2C%20I%20was%20doing%20freelance%20jobs%20here%20and%20there%2C%20and%20some%20more%20consistent%20stuff%20in%20the%20tech%20world.%20She%20was%20deep%20into%20her%20career%20as%20a%20content%20creator%20and%20needed%20help%20running%20her%20online%20business.%20She%20thought%20I'd%20be%20the%20perfect%20fit%20and%20asked%20if%20I%20would%20work%20for%20her.%20So%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20and%20became%20a%20full-time%20stay-at-home-boyfriend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20that%20I%20didn't%20enjoy%20my%20job%2C%20but%20this%20was%20just%20a%20greener%20pasture%20that%20I%20could%20step%20toward.%20It%20was%20an%20opportunity%20that%20was%20better%20suited%20to%20me%2C%20I%20think%2C%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20I%20was%20really%20into%20cooking%20and%20sewing%20before%20I%20even%20met%20Levi%2C%20and%20this%20meant%20I%20could%20focus%20on%20those%20interests%20more%20and%20hone%20my%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20no%20plans%20to%20return%20to%20the%209-to-5%20and%20would%20only%20do%20so%20if%20our%20online%20businesses%20stopped%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20started%20posting%20online%20to%20show%20the%20world%20a%20softer%20type%20of%20masculinity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202022%2C%20I%20started%20posting%20snippets%20of%20my%20life%20on%20TikTok.%20My%20videos%20mainly%20showcase%20the%20meals%20I%20cook%20for%20Levi%2C%20but%20sometimes%20it's%20me%20braiding%20her%20hair%2C%20hemming%20her%20clothes%2C%20or%20fixing%20things%20around%20the%20house.%20I'm%20soft-spoken%20and%20have%20a%20gentle%20manner%2C%20and%20the%20comments%20from%20my%20mainly%20female%20audience%20have%20been%20overwhelmingly%20positive.%20These%20are%20all%20things%20I%20do%20anyway%2C%20but%20it%20was%20Levi's%20idea%20to%20share%20it%20with%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20the%20time%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteachers-and-parents-talk-about-andrew-tates-influence-on-kids-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndrew%20Tate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20anti-feminist%20influencer%2C%20was%20really%20popular%2C%20and%20there%20was%20an%20oversaturation%20of%20toxic%20masculinity%20online.%20We%20saw%20this%20need%20and%20an%20opportunity%20to%20present%20a%20kind%2C%20loving%20man%20in%20the%20online%20space.%20One%20thing%20I'm%20very%20proud%20of%20is%20showing%20the%20duality%20a%20man%20can%20have.%20I%20have%20both%20feminine%20and%20masculine%20characteristics%2C%20but%20I'm%20still%20a%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20raised%20in%20a%20very%20nurturing%20household%20where%20both%20my%20parents%20worked%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthird-shift-iceland-women-are-tired-of-worrying-gender-equality-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esplit%20the%20domestic%20tasks%3C%2Fa%3E%20evenly.%20Everyone%20contributed%20to%20the%20household%2C%20and%20gender%20was%20never%20tied%20to%20a%20specific%20role%2C%20so%20living%20this%20way%20has%20never%20affected%20my%20sense%20of%20masculinity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22William%20Conrad%20holding%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660d882c3f923f7dab0424ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConrad%20has%20been%20a%20stay-at-home-boyfriend%20for%20three%20years.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Conrad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ESocial%20media%20is%20giving%20young%20men%20a%20skewed%20image%20of%20what%20women%20want%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20often%20comment%20things%20like%20%26quot%3BWhere%20do%20I%20buy%20mine%3F%26quot%3B%20on%20my%20content.%20And%20while%20it's%20always%20nice%20to%20hear%20that%20someone%20thinks%20I'm%20a%20good%20boyfriend%2C%20it's%20also%20sad%20that%20a%20loving%20dynamic%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20scarce%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELots%20of%20women%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20man%20who%20will%20cook%20them%20a%20nice%20meal%20and%20be%20gentle%2C%20but%20maybe%20not%20enough%20men%20value%20these%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-ways-toxic-masculinity-shows-up-in-your-relationship-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoxic%20masculinity%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20s