20look%20younger%20than%20their%20peers%20tend%20to%20report%20better%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsycnet.apa.org%2Ffulltext%2F2024-58254-001.html%5C%22%3EThe%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20led%20by%20Julie%20Ober%20Allen%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20health%20promotion%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Oklahoma%2C%20involved%20over%202%2C000%20US%20adults%20aged%2050%20to%2080.%20Participants%20were%20asked%20about%20their%20perception%20of%20their%20appearance%20compared%20to%20others%20their%20age%2C%20as%20well%20as%20any%20age-related%20experiences%20they%20had%2C%20positive%20or%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20participants%20believed%20they%20looked%20younger%20than%20their%20peers.%20Women%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20hold%20this%20belief%20than%20men%2C%20and%20they%20were%20also%20more%20likely%20to%20invest%20in%20maintaining%20a%20youthful%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20focusing%20solely%20on%20looking%20young%20may%20not%20be%20the%20healthiest%20approach.%20The%20study%20found%20that%20people%20who%20reported%20experiencing%20age%20discrimination%2C%20even%20with%20attempts%20to%20look%20younger%2C%20tended%20to%20report%20poorer%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20believe%20this%20highlights%20the%20negative%20impact%20of%20societal%20bias%20against%20ageing.%20They%20recommend%20focusing%20on%20healthy%20behaviours%20like%20exercise%20and%20a%20good%20diet%2C%20which%20can%20improve%20both%20health%20and%20appearance%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgeism%20is%20a%20form%20of%20discrimination%20that%20often%20manifests%20as%20micro-aggressions%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ou.edu%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024%2Ffebruary%2Ffrom-wrinkles-to-wisdom-new-research-explores-the-complex-relationship-between-age-appearance-and-health%5C%22%3EAllen%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BTelling%20an%20older%20person%20that%20they%20look%20good%20for%20their%20age%20or%20assuming%20they%20can't%20operate%20technology%20can%20actually%20cause%20them%20to%20have%20a%20fight%20or%20flight%20stress%20response.%20Sometimes%20they%20engage%20in%20coping%20behaviours%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20stress-eating%20candy%20or%20smoking%20a%20cigarette%2C%20for%20example-behaviours%20associated%20with%20negative%20health%20outcomes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20asked%20people%20how%20much%20time%20and%20energy%20they%20spend%20trying%20to%20look%20younger.%20It's%20a%20tricky%20question%20because%20it%20tends%20to%20activate%20some%20of%20those%20stereotypes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3B35%25%20of%20participants%20told%20us%20they%20invested%20time%20and%20money%20in%20these%20endeavors.%20Interestingly%2C%20these%20people%20reported%20both%20more%20positive%20and%20more%20negative%20experiences%20of%20ageing%20within%20a%20broader%20society.%20Perhaps%20those%20who%20tried%20and%20succeeded%20in%20looking%20younger%20experienced%20less%20discrimination.%20However%2C%20those%20same%20individuals%20may%20have%20also%20felt%20more%20anxious%20and%20uncomfortable%20with%20their%20ageing%20appearance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20positive%20self-perception%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20aging.%20By%20viewing%20ageing%20in%20a%20positive%20light%2C%20people%20may%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20adopt%20healthy%20habits%20that%20contribute%20to%20their%20overall%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712217240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fo0t9kcdo_age-appearance-and-health_625x300_04_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbelieving-you-look-younger-may-be-linked-to-better-health-study-suggests-5372444%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Researchers%20recommend%20focusing%20on%20healthy%20behaviours%20like%20exercise%20and%20a%20good%20diet%2C%20which%20can%20improve%20both%20health%20and%20appearance%20over%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbelieving-you-look-younger-may-be-linked-to-better-health-study-suggests-5372444%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbelieving-you-look-younger-may-be-linked-to-better-health-study-suggests-5372444%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbelieving-you-look-younger-may-be-linked-to-better-health-study-suggests-5372444%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia's%20adapting%20air%20defenses%20means%20Ukraine's%20new%20F-16s%20are%20an%20example%20of%20weapons%20that%20are%20'no%20longer%20relevant%3A'%20senior%20Ukrainian%20officer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225364%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Netherlands'%20Air%20Force%20F-16%20jetfighters%20participate%20in%20the%20NATO%20exercise%20as%20part%20of%20the%20NATO%20Air%20Policing%20mission%2C%20in%20Alliance%20members'%20sovereign%20airspace%20on%20July%204%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660e565b16bde8d4ead5847d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223419%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Dutch%20are%20set%20to%20give%20Ukraine%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20F-16s%20out%20of%20its%20aging%20stockpile.%3Cp%3EJOHN%20THYS%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20unnamed%20Ukrainian%20officer%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Farticle%2Fukraine-great-risk-front-line-collapse-war-russia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPolitico%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20his%20doubts%20about%20the%20usefulness%20of%20incoming%20F-16s.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20that%20Russia%20has%20already%20been%20preparing%20the%20battlefield%20for%20the%20NATO%20aircraft%20by%20range-finding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20an%20example%20of%20how%20Ukraine%20oft