3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20come%20when%20they're%20no%20longer%20relevant%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20this%20high-ranking%20officer%2C%20the%20Kremlin%20has%20been%20preparing%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-f-16-controls-flying-differ-from-ukraines-soviet-jets-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earrival%20of%20the%20F-16s%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20southern%20front%20by%20range-finding%20with%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20these%20missiles%2C%20fired%20without%20their%20warheads%2C%20are%20informing%20the%20Russians%20on%20how%20to%20best%20place%20their%20S-400%20defense%20systems%20to%20cover%20the%20frontline%20and%20limit%20where%20the%20F-16s%20can%20operate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20coalition%20of%20countries%20led%20by%20the%20US%2C%20Denmark%2C%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20has%20since%20mid-2023%20been%20training%20Ukrainian%20pilots%20to%20fly%20F-16s%2C%20and%20Kyiv%20is%20expected%20to%20soon%20receive%20up%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fus%2Fcomment%2F2024%2F01%2F03%2Fukraine-war-f16-fighter-jet-gripen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E60%20of%20the%20NATO%20aircraft%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-16s%20are%20expected%20to%20greatly%20increase%20Ukraine's%20strike%20capacity%20if%20fitted%20with%20long-range%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey've%20long%20been%20sought%20after%20by%20Kyiv%2C%20which%20hopes%20they%20can%20help%20Ukraine%20claw%20its%20way%20to%20air%20superiority%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20the%20arriving%20F-16s%20will%20be%20secondhand%20and%20likely%20several%20decades%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20pilot%20told%20Ukrainian%20media%20they're%20a%20massive%20step%20up%20from%20the%20Soviet%20MiGs%20he%20usually%20flies%2C%20comparing%20the%20upgrade%20to%20going%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-danish-f-16s-summer-russia-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Ba%20Nokia%2C%20straight%20to%20an%20iPhone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Politico's%20new%20report%20also%20sheds%20light%20on%20frustrations%20within%20Ukraine%20about%20the%20equipment%20its%20troops%20are%20receiving.%20The%20most%20prominent%20shortage%20is%20ammunition%20for%20the%20Western%20artillery%20and%20weapons%20that%20Kyiv%20received%20in%20the%20earlier%20days%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20shells%20running%20dry%2C%20Ukraine%20says%20it%20is%20struggling%20to%20make%20gains%20and%20hold%20back%20Russia's%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20this%20one%20officer's%20assessment%20is%20shared%20widely%20among%20Ukraine's%20forces%20and%20the%20country's%20military%20brass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVoice%20of%20America%2C%20owned%20by%20the%20US%20government%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.holosameryky.com%2Fa%2Fpilot-phantom-interview%2F7476726.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20an%20interview%20in%20February%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20Ukrainian%20pilot%20who%20said%20his%20comrades%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-pilots-training-f-16-jets-praise-aircraft-russia-war-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimpressed%20by%20the%20F-16s%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20found%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bexceeded%20their%20expectations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20another%20officer%20who%20spoke%20to%20Politico%20shared%20a%20philosophy%20about%20the%20war%20that%20reflected%20his%20colleague's%20F-16%20remarks%20%E2%80%94%20that%20weapons%20quickly%20become%20redundant%20once%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Russians%20are%20always%20studying%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%20%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20give%20us%20a%20second%20chance.%20And%20they're%20successful%20in%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cspan%3EUkrainian%20Air%20Force%20and%20Air%20Force%20Command%20%3C%2Fspan%3Edid%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20requ