%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Michael%20Page%20India%20Salary%20Guide%202024%2C%20there%20is%20a%20resurgence%20in%20hiring%20within%20traditional%20industries%2C%20particularly%20evident%20in%20the%20continued%20high%20demand%20for%20manufacturing%20and%20operations%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20there's%20a%20notable%20surge%20in%20the%20need%20for%20professionals%20skilled%20in%20data%20analytics%2C%20generative%20AI%2C%20and%20machine%20learning%20across%20various%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20guidance%20report%20covers%20the%20key%20sectors%20of%20BFSI%2C%20engineering%20%26amp%3B%20manufacturing%2C%20finance%20%26amp%3B%20accounting%2C%20healthcare%20%26amp%3B%20lifesciences%2C%20human%20resources%2C%20legal%2C%20compliance%2C%20procurement%20%26amp%3B%20supply%20chain%2C%20property%20%26amp%3B%20construction%2C%20sales%20%26amp%3B%20marketing%2C%20and%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20India's%206%20per%20cent%20GDP%20growth%20coupled%20with%20significant%20domestic%20investments%20and%20independence%20from%20external%20factors%2C%20positions%20India%20uniquely%20in%20the%20region%2C%20even%20amidst%20global%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20India's%20economy%20displaying%20such%20resilience%20and%20optimism%2C%20and%20surpassing%20its%20pre-COVID%20performance%2C%20the%20focus%20is%20now%20on%20harnessing%20this%20potential.%20Nurturing%20talent%20and%20fostering%20innovation%20thus%20remains%20a%20key%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ankit%20Agarwala%2C%20Managing%20Director%20at%20PageGroup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Agarwala%20further%20noted%20that%20the%20IT%20services%20industry%2C%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy%2C%20is%20witnessing%20a%20phase%20of%20recalibration.%20Companies%20are%20moderating%20their%20approach%20to%20salary%20increments%2C%20with%20expected%20hikes%20around%208%20per%20cent-10%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndustries%20like%20consumer%2C%20renewables%2C%20finance%2C%20and%20healthcare%20are%20flourishing%2C%20bolstered%20by%20investments%20from%20local%20and%20domestic%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Agarwala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESector-wise%20analysis%20showed%20that%20in%20IT%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%2C%20the%20hike%20range%20varies%20from%2035-45%20per%20cent%20for%20junior%20employees%2C%2030-40%20per%20cent%20hike%20for%20mid-level%20executives%2C%20and%2020-30%20per%20cent%20increment%20for%20senior%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20property%20and%20construction%20sector%20is%20offering%2020-40%20per%20cent%20hike%20to%20juniors%2C%2025-45%20per%20cent%20hike%20to%20middle-level%20executives%20and%20a%2020-40%20per%20cent%20salary%20appraisal%20to%20seniors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20delve%20deeper%20into%202024%2C%20the%20employment%20narrative%20in%20India%20is%20about%20more%20than%20just%20salaries.%20Flexibility%2C%20work%20culture%2C%20and%20professional%20growth%20opportunities%20are%20increasingly%20pivotal%20in%20job%20transitions%2C%20reflecting%20a%20maturing%20and%20holistic%20employment%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anshul%20Lodha%2C%20Managing%20Director%20at%20Page%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichael%20Page%20is%20a%20leading%20global%20recruitment%20firm%20specialising%20in%20permanent%2C%20contract%2C%20and%20temporary%20recruitment.%20Michael%20Page%20operates%20in%2037%20countries%20worldwide%20and%20has%20a%20strong%20presence%20in%20India.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712214780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fk89fgov_office-generic_625x300_08_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsenior-level-jobs-to-see-average-20-pay-hike-on-buoyant-econom