contract%20manufacturer%20of%20electronics.%20His%20wife%2C%20Savitha%20Ramesh%20joined%20the%20company%20in%201996%20and%20now%20serves%20as%20the%20company's%20chairperson.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERamesh%20Kunhikannan%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20India's%20historic%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20by%20supplying%20electronic%20systems%20to%20power%20both%20the%20rover%20and%20lander%2C%20which%20contributed%20to%20the%20mission's%20successful%20landing%20on%20the%20Moon's%20surface%20in%20August%202023.%20Chandrayaan-3%20was%20a%20mission%20led%20by%20ISRO%20with%20a%20budget%20of%20around%20%E2%82%B9615%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERamesh%20Kunhikannan%20has%2064%25%20stake%20in%20Kaynes%20Technology%20and%20share%20values%20of%20the%20company%20increased%20significantly%20after%20the%20success%20of%20Chandrayaan-3.%20This%20followed%20the%20company's%20already%20impressive%20performance%2C%20with%20its%20shares%20tripling%20in%20value%20since%20debuting%20on%20the%20share%20market%20in%20November%202022.%20Because%20of%20this%2C%20Mr%20Kunhikannan's%20net%20worth%20skyrocketed%2C%20reaching%20%241.2%20billion%20according%20to%20Forbes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712214600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fs2ltqs2_ramesh-kunhikannan_625x300_04_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeet-ramesh-kunhikannan-newly-minted-forbes-billionaire-who-supplied-equipment-to-chandrayaan-3-mission-5371815%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ramesh%20Kunhikannan%20has%20been%20named%20on%20the%20Forbes%20Billionaires%20List%202024%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20year.%20With%20an%20impressive%20net%20worth%20of%20%241.2%20billion%2C%20Mr%20Kunhikannan%20has%20secured%20his%20position%20among%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20richest%2