%20from%20wearing%20a%20wristband%20adorned%20with%20a%20religious%20symbol.%20The%20protesters%20claimed%20the%20act%20hurt%20religious%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20month%2C%20Christian%20schools%20in%20Assam%20received%20a%2015-day%20ultimatum%20from%20a%20radical%20Hindu%20group%20to%20remove%20all%20Christian%20symbols%20and%20religious%20habits%20worn%20by%20priests%2C%20nuns%2C%20and%20brothers%20on%20their%20campuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20key%20suggestions%20put%20forth%20by%20the%20CBCI%20for%20schools%20is%20the%20emphasis%20on%20respecting%20all%20faith%20traditions%20without%20discrimination.%20Educational%20institutions%20are%20urged%20not%20to%20impose%20Christian%20traditions%20on%20students%20of%20other%20religions%20and%20to%20establish%20an%20%26quot%3Binter-religious%20prayer%20room%26quot%3B%20on%20school%20premises%2C%20promoting%20inclusivity%20and%20religious%20tolerance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20student%20formation%2C%20the%20CBCI%20encourages%20schools%20to%20prioritise%20spiritual%20and%20moral%20growth%2C%20including%20activities%20such%20as%20prayer%2C%20retreats%2C%20and%20recitation%20of%20the%20Preamble%20to%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20during%20daily%20assemblies.%20The%20development%20of%20virtues%20and%20character%20traits%20such%20as%20resilience%2C%20humility%2C%20and%20leadership%20is%20also%20highlighted%20in%20the%2013-page%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20academic%20support%20and%20extracurricular%20activities%2C%20the%20guidelines%20stress%20the%20importance%20of%20mental%20health%20and%20well-being%2C%20advocating%20for%20counseling%20services%2C%20healthcare%20facilities%2C%20and%20awareness%20programs%20to%20address%20students'%20emotional%20and%20psychological%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20staff%20welfare%2C%20the%20CBCI%20recommends%20ongoing%20professional%20development%2C%20mentorship%20programs%2C%20and%20support%20services%20to%20ensure%20a%20heal