0to%20agriculture%20full-time%2C%20while%20Nagaratna%20and%20Malathi%20were%20working%20their%20full-time%20jobs%20in%20Bengaluru.%20During%20this%20conversation%2C%20Ravindra%20spoke%20of%20his%20travels%20around%20India%20while%20working%20for%20General%20Mills%2C%20reminiscing%20about%20missing%20his%20native%20Sankethi%20cuisine%20(from%20South-Western%20Karnataka)%20and%20expressing%20his%20desire%20to%20take%20this%20unique%20culinary%20tradition%20to%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20fate%20would%20have%20it%2C%20my%20aunt%20(Malathi)%20and%20parents%20(Ravindra%20and%20Nagaratna)%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20using%20my%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20%3Cem%3Erasam%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%20recipe%20to%20make%20small%20batches%20in%20a%2010%C3%9710%20square%20feet%20room%20and%20distribute%20it%20to%20family%20and%20friends.%20This%20was%20their%20%E2%80%98aha%E2%80%99%20moment%2C%20and%20the%20rest%2C%20as%20they%20say%2C%20is%20history%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharat%20Kaushik%2C%20director%20and%20CEO%20of%20Adukale%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20uninitiated%2C%20Adukale%20is%20a%20leading%20ready-to-cook%20(RTC)%20and%20ready-to-eat%20(RTE)%20brand%20that%20reflects%20the%20rich%20heritage%20of%20Sankethi%20cuisine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdukale%20was%20born%20out%20of%20sheer%20love%20and%20passion%20to%20bring%20time-tested%20Sankethi%20recipes%20to%20the%20fore.%20We%20gained%20significant%20popularity%20through%20word-of-mouth%2C%20owing%20to%20the%20immense%20popularity%20and%20demand%20for%20homegrown%20recipes.%20We%20moved%20on%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F246450%2Flakshmi-raj-grated-coconut-fresh-n-easy-kerala-instant-food-products-women-entrepreneur-buy-online-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20making%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20powders%3C%2Fa%3E%20and